@startuml
title Student Join Lesson — User Flow

actor Student as S
participant "LMS (Client)" as Client
participant "LMS (Server)" as LMS
participant "Media Server" as MS

S -> Client: Open lesson link
Client -> LMS: Request join(sessionId)
activate LMS
LMS -> MS: Authorize and add participant(sessionId)
MS --> LMS: Participant added
LMS --> Client: Join confirmation + streamUrl
deactivate LMS
Client -> MS: Connect to stream(streamUrl)
MS --> Client: Media stream

note over S,MS: Student receives media and can interact

@enduml
